==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Optometrist
<hw>Op*tom"e*trist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who is
skilled in or practices optometry, especially one who examines the eyes
for defects in vision and prescribes the proper lenses to correct any
defects discovered.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Optometry</ent>⟦br⟧
